title: Awkward
body: Oh. I mean, I guess I knew it was coming. All the mice do. My mom was injected with cancer and that's how she died. I just hope I get to go quickly.

title: Reassurance
body: That makes me feel better. You're a good friend. Us lab mice don't usually have friends for long, since we're experimented on so much.

title: Hope
body: Really? That makes me feel much better. You're a great friend. Us lab mice don't usually have friends for long, since we're experimented on so much.
